<subSubSection id="9BEE82B5E179D87BFF2204AAFD6EFDC9" pageId="17" pageNumber="218" type="etymology">
<paragraph id="D34BD13EE179D87BFF2204AAFD6EFDC9" blockId="17.[151,1436,151,680]" pageId="17" pageNumber="218">
<emphasis id="E1800D2CE179D87BFF2204AAFEE3FE24" bold="true" box="[199,334,476,501]" pageId="17" pageNumber="218">Etymology.</emphasis>
This species is named after our colleague, Elizabeth Morgulis, who has contributed to the senior author's research in many ways. It is an adjective.
</paragraph>
